---
// Stage 2 - Control MULTI-marcador (DEFINICION SIMULTANEA). En la fecha final, cuando hay
// DOS finales del mismo grupo vivos a la vez, el admin ve DOS controles lado a lado (uno
// por partido), cada uno escribiendo su propio marcador por matchId via setLiveScore /
// limpiando con clearLiveScore / finalizando con finalizeOfficialResult. Finalizar uno NO
// toca el otro (la RPC limpia solo la fila live de ese match).
//
// N=1 byte-igual: con un solo partido vivo, este panel queda OCULTO y el flujo diario
// sigue por el MiniLiveScoreControl single de siempre (saveLiveMatchState). Solo aparece
// con >=2 vivos simultaneos (resolveActiveWindow.isSimultaneous).
//
// SSR = cascaron oculto. El cuerpo lo pinta admin.client.js (initMultiLiveControls) en
// runtime por innerHTML, colgado del UNICO subscribeLiveData del admin (sin segundo canal,
// igual que F11). Por eso el CSS va is:global anclado a [data-live-controls] (el DOM nace
// por innerHTML y no recibe el scope de Astro; gotcha 1).
//
// GUARDRAIL: la escritura multi (setLiveScore/clearLiveScore) esta detras de
// MULTI_LIVE_WRITE_ENABLED. Hasta que el operador aplique la migracion multi-fila en remoto
// Y suba el flag (paso manual acoplado), Actualizar/Finalizar de este panel mostraran el
// error inline de guardrail. Es esperado: no rompe el N=1 diario.
---

<section
  class="live-controls"
  data-live-controls
  data-animate="fade-up"
  aria-labelledby="live-controls-title"
  hidden
>
  <header class="lc-head">
    <div>
      <span class="lc-eyebrow">DEFINICION SIMULTANEA</span>
      <h2 id="live-controls-title">Marcadores en vivo (par del grupo)</h2>
      <p class="lc-sub">
        Los dos finales del grupo se juegan a la vez. Pon cada uno en vivo con "Iniciar en
        vivo" y administralo por separado: actualizar y finalizar uno no afecta al otro.
      </p>
    </div>
    <p class="lc-feedback" data-live-controls-feedback role="status" aria-live="polite"></p>
  </header>

  <div class="lc-body" data-live-controls-body></div>
</section>

<style is:global>
  [data-live-controls] {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--pm-mint-500, #21d99a);
    border-radius: var(--pm-radius-lg, 16px);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pm-white, #fff), var(--pm-panel-soft, #f5f8fc));
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-head {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.5rem 1rem;
    align-items: flex-start;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-eyebrow {
    color: var(--pm-green-700, #1f7a52);
    font-family: var(--font-display, sans-serif);
    font-size: 0.6rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  [data-live-controls] h2 {
    margin: 0.1rem 0;
    font-family: var(--font-display, sans-serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    font-weight: 950;
    color: var(--pm-blue-900, #0b2545);
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-sub {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: var(--pm-text-soft, #4a5a72);
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-feedback {
    margin: 0;
    min-height: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.74rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--pm-green-700, #1f7a52);
  }

  /* Grupo de un par + grilla de controles */
  [data-live-controls] .lc-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.8rem;
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-group:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-group-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display, sans-serif);
    font-size: 0.62rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--pm-blue-700, #1f5fa6);
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(min(100%, 16rem), 1fr));
    gap: 0.7rem;
  }

  /* Tarjeta de control por partido */
  [data-live-controls] .lc-card {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.55rem;
    padding: 0.75rem 0.85rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--pm-mint-500, #21d99a);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    background: var(--pm-white, #fff);
    min-width: 0;
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-card[data-phase="official"] {
    border-color: var(--pm-border-soft, rgba(7, 26, 53, 0.18));
    background: var(--pm-panel-soft, #f5f8fc);
  }
  /* "POR INICIAR": preparable (aun no en vivo) -> azul, sin glow de vivo. */
  [data-live-controls] .lc-card[data-phase="ready"] {
    border-color: var(--pm-blue-500, #2f72d6);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pm-white, #fff), var(--pm-blue-50, #eef5fe));
  }

  [data-live-controls] .lc-card-head {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-dot {
    width: 0.6rem;
    height: 0.6rem;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--pm-mint-500, #21d99a);
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--pm-mint-500, #21d99a);
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-card[data-phase="official"] .lc-dot {
    background: var(--pm-text-soft, #4a5a72);
    box-shadow: none;
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-card[data-phase="ready"] .lc-dot {
    background: var(--pm-blue-500, #2f72d6);
    box-shadow: 0 0 8px var(--pm-blue-500, #2f72d6);
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-tag {
    padding: 0.1rem 0.4rem;
    border-radius: 999px;
    background: var(--pm-blue-100, #e3effb);
    color: var(--pm-blue-700, #1f5fa6);
    font-family: var(--font-display, sans-serif);
    font-size: 0.56rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-state {
    margin-left: auto;
    font-family: var(--font-display, sans-serif);
    font-size: 0.54rem;
    font-weight: 900;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-card[data-phase="live"] .lc-state { color: var(--pm-green-700, #1f7a52); }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-card[data-phase="ready"] .lc-state { color: var(--pm-blue-700, #1f5fa6); }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-card[data-phase="official"] .lc-state { color: var(--pm-text-soft, #4a5a72); }

  [data-live-controls] .lc-board {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) auto minmax(0, 1fr);
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-team {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.25rem;
    min-width: 0;
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-team-name {
    max-width: 100%;
    overflow: hidden;
    color: var(--pm-blue-900, #0b2545);
    font-family: var(--font-display, sans-serif);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    font-weight: 950;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-stepper { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.3rem; }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-score {
    min-width: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--pm-blue-950, #071a35);
    font-family: var(--font-display, sans-serif);
    font-size: 1.45rem;
    font-weight: 950;
    line-height: 1;
    text-align: center;
    font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-step {
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    width: 1.5rem;
    height: 1.5rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--pm-blue-500, #2f72d6);
    border-radius: var(--pm-radius-sm, 8px);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9);
    color: var(--pm-blue-700, #1f5fa6);
    font-family: var(--font-display, sans-serif);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    font-weight: 950;
    line-height: 1;
    cursor: pointer;
    user-select: none;
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-step.plus { border-color: var(--pm-mint-500, #21d99a); color: var(--pm-green-700, #1f7a52); }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-step:disabled { opacity: 0.4; cursor: not-allowed; }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-versus { color: var(--pm-text-soft, #4a5a72); font-weight: 900; }

  [data-live-controls] .lc-actions {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.3fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    gap: 0.4rem;
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-actions button {
    min-height: 2.2rem;
    padding: 0.45rem 0.6rem;
    border-radius: var(--pm-radius-sm, 8px);
    font-family: var(--font-display, sans-serif);
    font-size: 0.66rem;
    font-weight: 950;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    cursor: pointer;
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-update {
    border: 1px solid var(--pm-mint-500, #21d99a);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pm-mint-500, #21d99a), var(--pm-cyan-500, #18ddf2));
    color: #06251a;
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-update[data-saved="true"] {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--pm-green-700, #1f7a52), var(--pm-mint-500, #21d99a));
    color: #fff;
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-finalize {
    border: 1px solid var(--pm-blue-500, #2f72d6);
    background: var(--pm-white, #fff);
    color: var(--pm-blue-700, #1f5fa6);
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-clear {
    border: 1px solid var(--pm-border-soft, rgba(7, 26, 53, 0.18));
    background: var(--pm-white, #fff);
    color: var(--pm-text-soft, #4a5a72);
  }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-actions button:disabled { opacity: 0.5; cursor: not-allowed; }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-actions button:focus-visible { outline: none; box-shadow: var(--pm-focus-ring, 0 0 0 3px rgba(24, 221, 242, 0.6)); }
  [data-live-controls] .lc-official-note {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.66rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--pm-text-soft, #4a5a72);
  }
</style>
